ing, AUD/USD is quoted just slightly below its\nopening price at 1.0645, down from 1.0660. To the downside, Ms.\nBednarik finds support at 1.0620, 1.0580, 1.0550 and 1.0530, while\nto the upside, she expects selling interest to come in at 1.0670,\n1.0710 and 1.0755.\n<br />\n</p>\r\n\t\t\t</div>\r\n            \r\n            \r\n\t\t\t\t<p><em>The views and opinions expressed herein are the views and opinions of the author and do not necessarily reflect those of The NASDAQ OMX Group, Inc.</em></p>\r\n            \r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n<!-- START social section -->\r\n\t\t<div id="article-social">\r\n\t\t\t<div id="article-social-inner">\r\n\t\t        <div class="article-social-inner-text">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tDid you like this article? &nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n\t\t\t\t</div><!--end text-->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="google-plus-one-container">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<g:plusone size="medium" callback="" href="'http\\x3a\\x2f\\x2fcommunity.nasdaq.com\\x2fNews\\x2f2011-09\\x2fforex-audusd-favors-retest-of-10710-vbednarik.aspx\\x3fstoryid\\x3d93612'"></g:plusone>&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- end google plus one-->\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<!-- START facebook like iframe-->\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="facebook-container">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<iframe src="http://www.facebook.com/plugins/like.php?href=http%3a%2f%2fcommunity.nasdaq.com%2fNews%2f2011-09%2fforex-audusd-favors-retest-of-10710-vbednarik.aspx%3fstoryid%3d93612&amp;layout=button_count&amp;show_faces=true&amp;width=170&amp;action=recommend&amp;colorscheme=light&amp;height=21" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" style="border:none; vertical-align:middle; overflow:hidden; width:170px; height:21px;" allowTransparency="true"></iframe>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- END facebook like iframe-->\r\n\t\t    \t\r\n\t\t        <div class="tweet-meme-container">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<script type="text/javascript">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\ttweetmeme_style = 'compact';\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\ttweetmeme_source = 'nasdaq';\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\ttweetmeme_service = 'bit.ly';\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\tservice_api = 