5.html" >DC quality of work: what has the poll of forex traders shown?</a></div>\n\t\t\t<div class="pages-rating"><a class="right-link" href="http://www.profi-forex.us/news/entry4000001753.html" >Which Forex brokers offer the lowest spreads?</a></div>\n\t\t\t<div class="pages-rating"><a class="right-link" href="http://www.profi-forex.us/news/entry4000000221.html" >The US Crisis: âThe Great Depression of 1929-1933â</a></div>\n\t\t\t<div class="pages-rating"><a class="right-link" href="http://www.profi-forex.us/news/entry4000001763.html" >Scandal: why hasnât Ikon Group paid the profit to its trader?</a></div>\n\t\t\t<div class="pages-rating"><a class="right-link" href="http://www.profi-forex.us/news/entry4000001793.html" >Mobile Trading: Pros and Cons</a></div>\n\t\t\t<div class="pages-rating"><a class="right-link" href="http://www.profi-forex.us/news/entry4000001775.html" >For investors: does dollar have a future?</a></div>\n\t\t\t<div class="pages-rating"><a class="right-link" href="http://www.profi-forex.us/news/entry4000001864.html" >Non-payments of profit: brokers versus clients. Who is right?</a></div>\n\t\t\t<div class="pages-rating"><a class="right-link" href="http://www.profi-forex.us/news/entry4000001833.html" >Will Fed Res manage to stabilize US Dollar and global economy?</a></div>\n\t\t\t<div class="pages-rating"><a class="right-link" href="http://www.profi-forex.us/news/entry4000001849.html" >For investors: will oil get cheaper during the world crisis?</a></div>\n\t\t\t<div class="pages-rating"><a class="right-link" href="http://www.profi-forex.us/news/entry4000001771.html" >Mexico: backwater or slough for foreign investors?</a></div>\n\t\n\t\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\t\n<div id="cat-center">\n\t\t<h2 style="text-align:center;">Foreign exchange market</h2>\n\t\t<div id="news-item">\n\t\t<h3 style="text-align:center;"><em>EURUSD: ECB takes a break</em></h3>\t\n\t\t<p class='article-date'>09 September 03:52 AM</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img align="left" style="margin-bottom:10px;" src="http://www.profi-forex.us/system/news/101_267.jpg" width="320" height="214" alt="EURUSD"/><br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t <p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">Jean-Claude Trichet, President of the ECB, said during yesterday&rsquo;s press conference that the bank&rsquo;s experts had downgraded the forecast for the eurozone&rsquo;s economic growth from 1,5&mdash;2,3% down to 1,4&mdash;1,8% in 2011 and from 0,6&mdash;2,8% down to 0,4&mdash;2,2% in 2012, thus recognizing that the toughening of the ECB&rsquo;s monetary policy was a failure. However, the rate of inflation is relatively balanced.</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="page-break-after: always;"><span style="display: none;">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">Therefore, Jean-Claude Trichet gave everyone to understand that the ECB was going to take a timeout in the &ldquo;game&rdquo; of interest rate hikes. &nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">In April and July 2011 the ECB already increased the key interest rate after a prolonged downgrade (since 2008). In an interview with Bloomberg (Sep 6) Nouriel Roubini said: &ldquo;The ECB made its biggest mistake in its history hiking rates this year. They&rsquo;ve created more sovereign debt problems. They&rsquo;ve created more banking problems&hellip;&rdquo; Some other respected experts share his point of view.</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><b>FOREX.</b></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">According to the SRP Sub-department under the Department of <a href="http://www.masterforex-v.su">Masterforex-V trading system</a> , for EURUSD it is possible to consider the formation of the ABC retracement pattern of H1 with a chance of forming wave B H4 or elongating wave 5 H4.</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">For the 2<sup>nd</sup> scenario the closest target is 1.3809, with a chance of reaching 1.3751 and 1.3563.</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><img width="700" border="0" hspace="10" height="608" alt="" src="http://www.profi-forex.us/system/user_files/Images/News/09-2011/090911/resized/102_853194361.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">To define the vector of the forthcoming movement we apply the SRP elements and other binary patterns by MF.</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>You are free to discuss this article here: &nbsp;\r\n<a href="http://forum.masterforex-v.su/index.php?showforum=308">forum for traders and investors</a></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t<div class="clearthem" style="height:12px;"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id="author" >\n\t\t\t<strong>\n\t\t\t\tText:&nbsp;<em>Alex von Stachelkopf, the SRP Sub-department under the Department of Masterforex-V trading system</em>\n\t\t\t</strong>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id="zak">\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<div id="box" class="dialog"></div> \n<script type="text/javascript">\nvar complete = 0;\nfunction LoadAddToBlog() { html_loaded = 0; complete = 0; LoadPage('','','box','common/insert_to_blog','4625');  setTimeout('OpenModal()',100); }\nfunction OpenModal() { if (html_loaded == 1 && complete == 0) {\tsm('box',400,500);\thtml_loaded = 0; complete = 1; } else { setTimeout('OpenModal()',100); } }\n</script>\n<span class="dialink" onclick="LoadAddToBlog();" title="Add to blog"><img alt="Add to blog" src="img/blogger.png" width="16" height="16"/></span>\n<a target="_zakladka" style="padding-right:2px;" href="http://www.google.com/bookmarks/