-forex.us/system/news/101_266.jpg" width="320" height="202" alt="EURUSD"/><br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t <p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">Today at 16.00GMT the US President Barack Obama will give a speech to a joint session of the US Congress on economic prospects and unemployment. He is going to &quot;lay out a series of bipartisan proposals that the Congress can take immediately to continue to rebuild the American economy&quot;.</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="page-break-after: always;"><span style="display: none;">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">Other long-term goals are to reduce the budget deficit, to create new jobs, to expand tax benefits for small-scale businesses and to invest more funds in the US infrastructure. The project is planned to be financed at the expense of budget spending reduction.</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><b>FOREX.</b></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">According to the SRP Sub-department under the Department of <a href="http://www.masterforex-v.su">Masterforex-V trading system</a> , EURUSD has finished working out a downward RP (reversal point) of H4. At this point the currency pair is forming a wave of H1-H4, which may well be either the 4<sup>th</sup> sub-wave of the downswing form 1.4548 or wave B.</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">In the 1<sup>st</sup> scenario the price may hit 1.3809, in the 2<sup>nd</sup> one it is necessary to monitor the momentum structure of the downswing.</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="/system/user_files/Images/News/09-2011/080911/102.jpg" rel="lightbox-cats"><img width="700" hspace="10" height="577" border="0" alt="" src="http://www.profi-forex.us/system/user_files/Images/News/09-2011/080911/resized/102_2277088954.jpg" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">To define the vector of the forthcoming movement we apply the SRP elements and other binary patterns by MF.</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>You are free to discuss this article here: &nbsp;\r\n<a href="http://forum.masterforex-v.su/index.php?showforum=308">forum for traders and investors</a></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t<div class="clearthem" style="height:12px;"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id="author" >\n\t\t\t<strong>\n\t\t\t\tText:&nbsp;<em>Alex von Stachelkopf, the SRP Sub-department under the Department of Masterforex-V trading system</em>\n\t\t\t</strong>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id="zak">\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<div id="box" class="dialog"></div> \n<script type="text/javascript">\nvar complete = 0;\nfunction LoadAddToBlog() { html_loaded = 0; complete = 0; LoadPage('','','box','common/insert_to_blog','4621');  setTimeout('OpenModal()',100); }\nfunction OpenModal() { if (html_loaded == 1 && complete == 0) {\tsm('box',400,500);\thtml_loaded = 0; complete = 1; } else { setTimeout('OpenModal()',100); } }\n</script>\n<span class="dialink" onclick="LoadAddToBlog();" title="Add to blog"><img alt="Add to blog" src="img/blogger.png" width="16" height="16"/></span>\n<a target="_zakladka" style="padding-right:2px;" href="http://www.google.com/bookmarks/mark?op=add&bkmk=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.profi-forex.us%2Fnews%2Fentry4000001870.html&title=EURUSD prospects against the background of President Obamaâs speech" title="Save this page on Google" ><img src="img/icon_google.png" alt="" width="16" height="16" /></a>\n<a target="_zakladka" style="padding-right:2px;" href="http://twitter.com/home?status=EURUSD prospects against the background of President Obamaâs speech