t" src="http://www.profi-forex.us/system/news/resized/cotton_1_3517244232.jpg" width="75" height="50" alt="" /></a>\n\t\t\t\t<a href="http://www.profi-forex.us/news/entry4000001877.html">Cotton market outlook: prices hit record</a>\t\n</div>\n<div class="hot-all">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href="http://www.profi-forex.us/news/entry4000001876.html"><img align="left" src="http://www.profi-forex.us/system/news/resized/A07-4_9_3800725591.jpg" width="75" height="44" alt="" /></a>\n\t\t\t\t<a href="http://www.profi-forex.us/news/entry4000001876.html">Nouriel Roubini: global crisis threat is real</a>\t\n</div>\n<div class="hot-all">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href="http://www.profi-forex.us/news/entry4000001875.html"><img align="left" src="http://www.profi-forex.us/system/news/resized/A09-1_12_1775510013.jpg" width="54" height="75" alt="" /></a>\n\t\t\t\t<a href="http://www.profi-forex.us/news/entry4000001875.html">GBPUSD: volatility outlook for Sep 9th 2011</a>\t\n</div>\n\n<div class="clearthem"  style="height:17px;"></div>\n\t\t\t<div class="hr"></div>\t\t\n\t\t<div align="center" style="padding-top:10px;">\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t</div>\n\t\n\t<div style="height:10px;"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class="news-list-item">\n\t\t\t\t<h4>GBPUSD: volatility outlook for Sep 9th 2011</h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img align="right" src="http://www.profi-forex.us/system/news/resized/A09-1_12_3210572180.jpg" width="64" height="90" alt="" />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Yesterday&rsquo;s trading session was rather volatile, thus giving volatility  buyers an opportunity to make money. As expected, the BoE and ECB&rsquo;s  interest rates decision, the US and eurozone&rsquo;s trade balance and the US  jobless claims were the main market drivers. President Obama and  Jean-Claude Trichet&rsquo;s speeches were yesterday&rsquo;s key events.</p>\n\t\t\t\t<div class="clearthem"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class='pub-date'><strong>Publication date:&nbsp;<em>09 September 04:12 AM</em></strong></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class='read-more'><a style="line-height:12px;" href="http://www.profi-forex.us/news/entry4000001875.html">Read&nbsp;more&nbsp;&#187;</a></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class="clearthem"></div>\n\t\t\t</div>\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class="news-list-item">\n\t\t\t\t<h4>EURUSD: ECB takes a break</h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img align="right" src="http://www.profi-forex.us/system/news/resized/101_267_3640229136.jpg" width="90" height="61" alt="" />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">Jean-Claude Trichet, President of  the ECB, said during yesterday&rsquo;s press conference that the bank&rsquo;s  experts had downgraded the forecast for the eurozone&rsquo;s economic growth  from 1,5&mdash;2,3% down to 1,4&mdash;1,8% in 2011 and from 0,6&mdash;2,8% down to  0,4&mdash;2,2% in 2012, thus recognizing that the toughening of the ECB&rsquo;s  monetary policy was a failure. However, the rate of inflation is  relatively balanced.</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class="clearthem"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class='pub-date'><strong>Publication date:&nbsp;<em>09 September 03:52 AM</em></strong></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class='read-more'><a style="line-height:12px;" href="http://www.profi-forex.us/news/entry4000001874.html">Read&nbsp;more&nbsp;&#187;</a></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class="clearthem"></div>\n\t\t\t</div>\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class="news-list-item">\n\t\t\t\t<h4>Coffee market: investors anticipate lower prices</h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img align="right" src="http://www.profi-forex.us/system/news/resized/A08-9_11_4166376194.jpg" width="90" height="68" alt="" />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The record-breaking production of coffee in Brazil managed to suspend  the rally in the &ldquo;Arabica coffee&rdquo; market. The growth had reached 50%.  Another factor suspending the growth was the expected increase in  Columbia&rsquo;s export.</p>\n\t\t\t\t<div class="clearthem"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class='pub-date'><strong>Publication date:&nbsp;<em>08 September 07:37 AM</em></strong></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class='read-more'><a style="line-height:12px;" href="http://www.profi-forex.us/news/entry4000001873.html">Read&nbsp;more&nbsp;&#187;</a></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class="clearthem"></div>\n\t\t\t</div>\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class="news-list-item">\n\t\t\t\t<h4>GBPUSD: volatility outlook for Sep 8th 2011</h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img align="right" src="http://www.profi-forex.us/system/news/resized/A08-4_12_448324778.jpg" width="90" height="90" alt="" />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Yesterday the market was relatively calm. There was practically no  significant news. As expected, the level of volatility declined a  little. The currency pair rebounded from the main option barrier  (1.5911) and rallied, passing almost 100 points.</p>\n\t\t\t\t<div class="clearthem"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class='pub-date'><strong>Publication date:&nbsp;<em>08 September 04:52 AM</em></strong></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class='read-more'><a style="line-height:12px;" href="http://www.profi-forex.us/news/entry4000001872.html">Read&nbsp;more&nbsp;&#187;</a></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class="clearthem"></div>\n\t\t\t</div>\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class="news-list-item">\n\t\t\t\t<h4>EURUSD: Italy on strike</h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img align="right" src="http://www.profi-forex.us/system/news/resized/c6604f1f070c_2778466048.jpg" width="90" height="60" alt="" />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Italy&rsquo;s main trade union has called a strike. Thousands of people joined  the strike, protesting against the economic steps taken by the Italian  government. Italians keeps opposing the decision to reduce the budget by  &euro;70B. Moreover, the Italian authorities are considering another round  of belt tightening (&euro;45B).</p>\n\t\t\t\t<div class="clearthem"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class='pub-date'><strong>Publication date:&nbsp;<em>08 September 04:10 AM</em></strong></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class='read-more'><a style="line-height:12px;" href="http://www.profi-forex.us/news/entry4000001871.html">Read&nbsp;more&nbsp;&#187;</a></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class="clearthem"></div>\n\t\t\t</div>\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class="news-list-item">\n\t\t\t\t<h4>USDCAD: Canada may see economic decline</h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img align="right" src="http://www.profi-forex.us/system/news/resized/flag_1_573802800.jpg" width="90" height="63" alt="" />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>According to Statistics Canada, the country&rsquo;s economy may face a decline  for the first time since the global crisis. By now it is the 2<sup>nd</sup>  G7 member with declining economic indicators. Before that Japan was the  only G7 member to have serious economic problems due to the natural and  nuclear disasters that hit the country earlier this year.</p>\n\t\t\t\t<div class="clearthem"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class='pub-date'><strong>Publication date:&nbsp;<em>07 September 05:21 PM</em></strong></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class='read-more'><a style="line-height:12px;" href="http://www.profi-forex.us/news/entry4000001869.html">Read&nbsp;more&nbsp;&#187;</a></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class="clearthem"></div>\n\t\t\t</div>\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class="news-list-item">\n\t\t\t\t<h4>6EU1 and ÐUR/USD keep declining</h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img align="right" src="http://www.profi-forex.us/system/news/resized/A07-23_8_573802800.jpg" width="90" height="63" alt="" />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Despite yesterday&rsquo;s roller coaster, EURUSD is still moving within a range.</p>\n\t\t\t\t<div class="clearthem"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class='pub-date'><strong>Publication date:&nbsp;<em>07 September 10:50 AM</em></strong></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class='read-more'><a style="line-height:12px;" href="http://www.profi-forex.us/news/entry4000001868.html">Read&nbsp;more&nbsp;&#187;</a></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class="clearthem"></div>\n\t\t\t</div>\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class="news-list-item">\n\t\t\t\t<h4>GBPUSD: volatility outlook for Sep 7th 2011</h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img align="right" src="http://www.profi-forex.us/system/news/resized/gbp3_4166376194.jpg" width="90" height="68" alt="" />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>As expected, yesterday&rsquo;s news background failed to increase the  volatility of GBPUSD. The British Pound was gradually losing its ground.  The currency pair passed more than 200pts down and broke below 1.5999  but rebounded from 1.5911. The expected volatility remained high.</p>\n\t\t\t\t<div class="clearthem"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class='pub-date'><strong>Publication date:&nbsp;<em>07 September 03:40 AM</em></strong></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class='read-more'><a style="line-height:12px;" href="http://www.profi-forex.us/news/entry4000001866.html">Read&nbsp;more&nbsp;&#187;</a></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class="clearthem"></div>\n\t\t\t</div>\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class="news-list-item">\n\t\t\t\t<h4>Non-payments of profit: brokers versus clients. Who is right?</h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img align="right" src="http://www.profi-forex.us/system/news/resized/profit_1907498273.jpg" width="90" height="66" alt="" />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Recently numerous brokers have been reluctant to pay profits to their clients. <a href="http://www.masterforex-v.su">Masterforex-V Academy</a>, Europe&rsquo;s best Forex-training project in 2009-2011, have already <span>counted  8 cases of non-payments to the Academy&rsquo;s students. The other 4 cases  aren&rsquo;t made public as the brokers and the traders have compromised  through intermediary of <a href="http://www.masterforex-v.su">Masterforex-V Academy</a>. </span></p>\n\t\t\t\t<div class="clearthem"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class='pub-date'><strong>Publication date:&nbsp;<em>06 September 02:38 PM</em></strong></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class='read-more'><a style="line-height:12px;" href="http://www.profi-forex.us/news/entry4000001864.html">Read&nbsp;more&nbsp;&#187;</a></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class="clearthem"></div>\n\t\t\t</div>\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class="news-list-item">\n\t\t\t\t<h4>Swiss National Bank pegs Franc to Euro</h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img align="right" src="http://www.profi-forex.us/system/news/resized/franki_4_2778466048.jpg" width="90" height="60" alt="" /